window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When you’re fighting for your lives, you have a choice. Get strong or die.</p> <p>The Hangsane are coming at Josh and the Misfits like a raging beast, and it's relentless. Having discovered the lost city of Telemar and found the Angel Stone, they find themselves trapped in the drow castle. If they can break free, they’ll have to fight their way across the mountains.</p> <p>But are they strong enough to survive?</p> <p>One thing’s for sure, if they don’t learn how to even up the playing field, they’ll be monster fodder before they get too far south.</p>"; 
